title: ProMaster Digital Elite Hobbyist Bag 8752 Overview
description:
Buy ProMaster Black Digital Elite Hobbyist Bag - 8752 - http://www.abt.com/product/84882/ProMaster-8752.html

The Digital Elite Hobbyist was designed for a digital or 35mm SLR. The Hide-A-Way compartment keeps memory cards filters and spare batteries organized and easily accessible. Carry this bag by the soft padded comfort handle or use as a waist pack.
Specifications:
• Deluxe extra comfort padded handle
• Soft tricot interior to protect LCD surfaces
• Heavy duty welded D-ring hardware
• Strong ballistic nylon construction with water resistant coatings
• Rain jacket for all weather protection
• Double layered closed cell foam for the ultimate protection
• Deluxe convertible waistpack design
• Anti abrasion panel to protect your clothing
• Easy access front accessory pouch with inside pockets and zippered mesh pouches
• Special interior accessory compartment
